Subject: [M148] media/gpu/v4l2IP: Remove input USERPTR support

Original change's description:
> media/gpu/v4l2IP: Remove input USERPTR support
>
> `V4L2_MEMORY_USERPTR` in V4L2ImageProcessor is no longer used
> today because the other image processors are used for
> v4l2 video encoding pre-processing.
